# Title: NoYouTubeAds (DNS)
# Description: DNS-level blocklist for YouTube advertising domains. For use with AdGuard Home, Pi-hole, or other DNS-level ad blockers.
# Version: 20260322.1
# Last Modified: 2026-03-22
# Source: https://github.com/jerryn70/GoodbyeAds, https://big.oisd.nl, uBlock Origin, EasyList
# License: MIT
#
# NOTE: This list only contains DNS-blockable domains (||domain^ syntax).
# For browser extension use with element hiding and scriptlets, use NoYouTubeAds instead.
#
# IMPORTANT: YouTube ads are increasingly served from the same domains as content.
# DNS-level blocking alone cannot block all YouTube video ads. For complete
# ad blocking, use a browser extension like uBlock Origin with NoYouTubeAdsFull.
#
